        <div class="msgSubject">Why I wouldn't recommend Aion...</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-08-11 00:39:34 | Edited: Aug 11 2010 12:42am  | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-128150877478319224" id="quote-128150877478319224" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-128150877478319224" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=157&amp;mid=128150877478319224&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=128150877478319224&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_128150877478319224" onclick="followToggle('add','128150877478319224')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
